<lb ed="B" n="0175a20"/><p xml:id="pB29p0175a2001" style="margin-left:1em">在郭城高橋門外東城丹陽鄉西去所領光相寺五厘
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B29.0160.0175b" n="0175b"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0175b01"/>北去正陽門五十里</p>
<lb ed="B" n="0175b02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">殿堂</cb:mulu><head>【殿堂】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">山門</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0175b0203" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">山門<note place="inline">參楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">天王殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0175b0207" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">天王殿<note place="inline">參楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">正佛殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0175b0212" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">正佛殿<note place="inline">參楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">觀音殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0175b0217" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">觀音殿<note place="inline">伍楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">方丈</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0175b0222" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">方丈<note place="inline">參楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">僧院</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0175b0226" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">僧
